config APP_SNAKE
    bool "Snake"
    default y
    depends on LIB_SEL4 && HAVE_LIBC && LIB_REFOS
    help
        Snake game for RefOS. Drawing done using ANSI.
        The Snake game is a demo for RefOS, showcasing UNIX-like dataspace
        printf, input functionality, and timer sleep functionality.
